@host = http://localhost:5182

### Create invoice with items in one transaction
POST {{host}}/api/invoices
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "invoiceDate": "2026-04-09T00:00:00",
  "notes": "Second invoice",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 2,
      "unitPrice": 150.00
    },
    {
      "productId": 2,
      "quantity": 1,
      "unitPrice": 45.00
    }
  ]
}

### Get invoice by id
GET {{host}}/api/invoices/8

### Issue invoice
POST {{host}}/api/invoices/8/issue